    "description": "诺德要塞：起源是一款专为追求高重玩性和无尽组合的策略爱好者量身打造的塔防游戏。在亲身打理中世纪北欧村庄的乐趣中放松身心，同时享受深入的战术游戏体验，轻松上手又挑战满满。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/82a9bd810c0a013b32d5ea6df0b276fb.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/82a9bd810c0a013b32d5ea6df0b276fb.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/82a9bd810c0a013b32d5ea6df0b276fb.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >20波挑战</h2>体验独特的诺德要塞体验，直面20波次的冷血强敌。直面不断升级的挑战、试炼您的战术能力，建设、制定战略并保卫诺德要塞。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展领地经济</h2>掌控14座具有独特升级和元成长的建筑，体验多样化的战略发展选择，纵横捭阖、在经济增长和保卫家园之间取得完美平衡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/fbb865c274921a4e160807bf6d0026bf.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/fbb865c274921a4e160807bf6d0026bf.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/fbb865c274921a4e160807bf6d0026bf.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造塔楼</h2>选择5座具有独特能力和无数个性化选项的塔楼。精密调整防护战术，步步为营、牢不可破。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/e468757aa171cb11f29cbe773a3541dc.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/e468757aa171cb11f29cbe773a3541dc.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/e468757aa171cb11f29cbe773a3541dc.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制升级</h2>探索80多种定制升级，体验丰富的个性化定制选项，增强战略纵深、开拓无数组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/93756ec48dc03310273c3ad5967e190a.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/93756ec48dc03310273c3ad5967e190a.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/93756ec48dc03310273c3ad5967e190a.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄，遗物，法术和更多</h2>从众多英雄组合中进行选择，保卫诺德要塞。遗物可以为您提供战略奖励，促进经济增长、提升防御能力，而法术则可以释放强大的效果，在危急时刻力挽狂澜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/1e5686c858418a10ee7e55c0b2e21e95.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/1e5686c858418a10ee7e55c0b2e21e95.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/1e5686c858418a10ee7e55c0b2e21e95.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激战升级</h2>利用协同效应，谨慎战略决策，提升自身的力量，征服一波又一波日益强大的敌人以及来势汹汹的领袖。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/dbcf53a23863036da76af14c9d2981d7.poster.avif?t=1738782102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/dbcf53a23863036da76af14c9d2981d7.webm?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086510/extras/dbcf53a23863036da76af14c9d2981d7.mp4?t=1738782102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排行榜头筹</h2>在排位系统中与好友一较高下，或者与全世界的玩家同台竞技。您能将人人梦寐以求的英灵殿排位斩获囊中吗？",
